		<h1>Ford Windstar</h1>
		<div id="subtitle">
			<h2>Model Year Comparison</h2>
		</div>
	</div> <!-- end #pageheader -->

	<div id="primary">
		<div id="intro">
			<dl>
							<dt>Worst Model Year:</dt>
				<dd id="worstyear">2003</dd>
				<dt>Worst Complaint:</dt>
				<dd id="worstcomplaints"><a href="/Ford/Windstar/2003/">transmission failure</a></dd>

			</dl>
			<p>Here are the Ford Windstars that have the most problems reported over the last 9 years.</p>
			<p>The <a href="/Ford/Windstar/2000/">2000 Ford Windstar</a> has the most complaints, &amp; the most-reported problem is with the <a href="/Ford/Windstar/2003/">2003 Windstar</a> for <a href="/Ford/Windstar/2003/transmission/transmission_failure.shtml"><em>transmission failure</em></a>.</p>
